bdBoyD_Ve0CpKlSyHp3j9aC0OYpmygKP6PeO8iO-1MYXDvElMc2_LccIeK-UL5E8QOyruEQhw-xNj4dkFXMAbw72qQogzMXZgP4FQ\" );\"\"=\"\">☑️</span></span>CSS / CSS3 :&nbsp;<span style=\"\" open=\"\" sans\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 16px;=\"\" display:=\"\" inline=\"\" !important;\"=\"\">CSS stands for&nbsp;</span><em style=\"\" open=\"\" sans\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 16px;\"=\"\">Cascading Style Sheet.&nbsp;</em><span style=\"\" open=\"\" sans\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 16px;=\"\" display:=\"\" inline=\"\" !important;\"=\"\">It will add look and styles to the HTML tags and as a result, the site looks and feels good. We cannot do styling with HTML tags; this is why we have to use CSS.&nbsp;</span><br style=\"\" open=\"\" sans\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 16px;\"=\"\"><span class=\"_5mfr\" style=\"margin: 0px 1px; font-family: inherit;\"><span class=\"_6qdm\" style=\"background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: contain; text-shadow: none; vertical-align: text-bottom; font-family: inherit; height: 16px; width: 16px; font-size: 16px; background-image: url(\" \");\"=\"\" https:=\"\" static.xx.fbcdn.net=\"\" images=\"\" emoji.php=\"\" v9=\"\" t8d=\"\" 1=\"\" 16=\"\" 2611.png?_nc_eui2=\"AeGeogbDJbdBoyD_Ve0CpKlSyHp3j9aC0OYpmygKP6PeO8iO-1MYXDvElMc2_LccIeK-UL5E8QOyruEQhw-xNj4dkFXMAbw72qQogzMXZgP4FQ\" );\"\"=\"\">☑️</span></span>&nbsp;Bootstrap :&nbsp;<span style=\"\" open=\"\" sans\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 16px;=\"\" display:=\"\" inline=\"\" !important;\"=\"\">It\'s a framework which is used for designing a website or web page. It contains HTML and CSS based design templates.&nbsp;</span><br><span class=\"_5mfr\" style=\"margin: 0px 1px; font-family: inherit;\"><span class=\"_6qdm\" style=\"background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: contain; text-shadow: none; vertical-align: text-bottom; font-family: inherit; height: 16px; width: 16px; font-size: 16px; background-image: url(\" \");\"=\"\" https:=\"\" static.xx.fbcdn.net=\"\" images=\"\" emoji.php=\"\" v9=\"\" t8d=\"\" 1=\"\" 16=\"\" 2611.png?_nc_eui2=\"AeGeogbDJbdBoyD_Ve0CpKlSyHp3j9aC0OYpmygKP6PeO8iO-1MYXDvElMc2_LccIeK-UL5E8QOyruEQhw-xNj4dkFXMAbw72qQogzMXZgP4FQ\" );\"\"=\"\">☑️</span></span>&nbsp;JQuery :&nbsp;<span style=\"\" open=\"\" sans\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 16px;=\"\" display:=\"\" inline=\"\" !important;\"=\"\">&nbsp;is a collection of JavaScript library functions. It is also open source and mostly it is designed to simplify the client-side scripting of HTML. The main purpose of jQuery is to provide an easy way to use JavaScript on websites to make them more interactive and attractive.&nbsp;</span><br>Backend Developer:&nbsp;<br><span class=\"_5mfr\" style=\"margin: 0px 1px; font-family: inherit;\"><span class=\"_6qdm\" style=\"background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: contain; text-shadow: none; vertical-align: text-bottom; font-family: inherit; height: 16px; width: 16px; font-size: 16px; background-image: url(\" \");\"=\"\" https:=\"\" static.xx.fbcdn.net=\"\" images=\"\" emoji.php=\"\" v9=\"\" t8d=\"\" 1=\"\" 16=\"\" 2611.png?_nc_eui2=\"AeGeogbDJbdBoyD_Ve0CpKlSyHp3j9aC0OYpmygKP6PeO8iO-1MYXDvElMc2_LccIeK-UL5E8QOyruEQhw-xNj4dkFXMAbw72qQogzMXZgP4FQ\" );\"\"=\"\">☑️</span></span>&nbsp;PHP Basics&nbsp;<br><span class=\"_5mfr\" style=\"margin: 0px 1px; font-family: inherit;\"><span class=\"_6qdm\" style=\"background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: contain; text-shadow: none; vertical-align: text-bottom; font-family: inherit; height: 16px; width: 16px; font-size: 16px; background-image: url(\" \");\"=\"\" https:=\"\" static.xx.fbcdn.net=\"\" images=\"\" emoji.php=\"\" v9=\"\" t8d=\"\" 1=\"\" 16=\"\" 2611.png?_nc_eui2=\"AeGeogbDJbdBoyD_Ve0CpKlSyHp3j9aC0OYpmygKP6PeO8iO-1MYXDvElMc2_LccIeK-UL5E8QOyruEQhw-xNj4dkFXMAbw72qQogzMXZgP4FQ\" );\"\"=\"\">☑️</span></span>&nbsp;PHP Advanced&nbsp;<br><span class=\"_5mfr\" style=\"margin: 0px 1px; font-family: inherit;\"><span class=\"_6qdm\" style=\"background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: contain; text-shadow: none; vertical-align: text-bottom; font-family: inherit; height: 16px; width: 16px; font-size: 16px; background-image: url(\" \");\"=\"\" https:=\"\" static.xx.fbcdn.net=\"\" images=\"\" emoji.php=\"\" v9=\"\" t8d=\"\" 1=\"\" 16=\"\" 2611.png?_nc_eui2=\"AeGeogbDJbdBoyD_Ve0CpKlSyHp3j9aC0OYpmygKP6PeO8iO-1MYXDvElMc2_LccIeK-UL5E8QOyruEQhw-xNj4dkFXMAbw72qQogzMXZgP4FQ\" );\"\"=\"\">☑️</span></span>&nbsp;Mysql :&nbsp;<span style=\"\" open=\"\" sans\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 16px;=\"\" display:=\"\" inline=\"\" !important;\"=\"\">A database is&nbsp;a structured set of data held in a computer. There many databases such as MS-SQL Server, MySQL Server, Oracle. based on the requirement we have to choose.</span><br><span class=\"_5mfr\" style=\"margin: 0px 1px; font-family: inherit;\"><span class=\"_6qdm\" style=\"background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: contain; text-shadow: none; vertical-align: text-bottom; font-family: inherit; height: 16px; width: 16px; font-size: 16px; background-image: url(\" \");\"=\"\" https:=\"\" static.xx.fbcdn.net=\"\" images=\"\" emoji.php=\"\" v9=\"\" t8d=\"\" 1=\"\" 16=\"\" 2611.png?_nc_eui2=\"AeGeogbDJbdBoyD_Ve0CpKlSyHp3j9aC0OYpmygKP6PeO8iO-1MYXDvElMc2_LccIeK-UL5E8QOyruEQhw-xNj4dkFXMAbw72qQogzMXZgP4FQ\" );\"\"=\"\">☑️</span></span>&nbsp;Ajax :&nbsp;<span style=\"\" open=\"\" sans\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 16px;=\"\" display:=\"\" inline=\"\" !important;\"=\"\">Asynchronous JavaScript And XML (AJAX) is a technique for creating better, faster, and more interactive web applications with the help of XML, HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.</span><br><span class=\"_5mfr\" style=\"margin: 0px 1px; font-family: inherit;\"><span class=\"_6qdm\" style=\"background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: contain; text-shadow: none; vertical-align: text-bottom; font-family: inherit; height: 16px; width: 16px; font-size: 16px; background-image: url(\" \");\"=\"\" https:=\"\" static.xx.fbcdn.net=\"\" images=\"\" emoji.php=\"\" v9=\"\" t8d=\"\" 1=\"\" 16=\"\" 2611.png?_nc_eui2=\"AeGeogbDJbdBoyD_Ve0CpKlSyHp3j9aC0OYpmygKP6PeO8iO-1MYXDvElMc2_LccIeK-UL5E8QOyruEQhw-xNj4dkFXMAbw72qQogzMXZgP4FQ\" );\"\"=\"\">☑️</span></span>&nbsp;Security<br><span class=\"_5mfr\" style=\"margin: 0px 1px; font-family: inherit;\"><span class=\"_6qdm\" style=\"background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: contain; text-shadow: none; vertical-align: text-bottom; font-family: inherit; height: 16px; width: 16px; font-size: 16px; background-image: url(\" \");\"=\"\" https:=\"\" static.xx.fbcdn.net=\"\" images=\"\" emoji.php=\"\" v9=\"\" t8d=\"\" 1=\"\" 16=\"\" 2611.png?_nc_eui2=\"AeGeogbDJbdBoyD_Ve0CpKlSyHp3j9aC0OYpmygKP6PeO8iO-1MYXDvElMc2_LccIeK-UL5E8QOyruEQhw-xNj4dkFXMAbw72qQogzMXZgP4FQ\" );\"\"=\"\">☑️</span></span>&nbsp;OOP :&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; display: inline !important;\">Object-oriented programming (OOP) is a programming language model organized around objicts</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; display: inline !important;\">&nbsp;rather than \"actions\" and data rather than logic. Historically, a program has been viewed as a logical procedure that takes input data, processes it, and produces output data.</span><br><span class=\"_5mfr\" style=\"margin: 0px 1px; font-family: inherit;\"><span class=\"_6qdm\" style=\"background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: contain; text-shadow: none; vertical-align: text-bottom; font-family: inherit; height: 16px; width: 16px; font-size: 16px; background-image: url(\" \");\"=\"\" https:=\"\" static.xx.fbcdn.net=\"\" images=\"\" emoji.php=\"\" v9=\"\" t8d=\"\" 1=\"\" 16=\"\" 2611.png?_nc_eui2=\"AeGeogbDJbdBoyD_Ve0CpKlSyHp3j9aC0OYpmygKP6PeO8iO-1MYXDvElMc2_LccIeK-UL5E8QOyruEQhw-xNj4dkFXMAbw72qQogzMXZgP4FQ\" );\"\"=\"\">☑️</span></span>&nbsp;Laravel Framework :&nbsp;</span><span style=\"\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" \"hiragino=\"\" kaku=\"\" gothic=\"\" pro\",=\"\" meiryo,=\"\" serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 15px;=\"\" display:=\"\" inline=\"\" !important;\"=\"\">It’s a structure that provides one with the capability to choose and create a program on it. Framework do help one to figure out how you shape your software and connect it with different Application program Interface(APIs). The framework is a set of classes that do makes developers life easier. A good example is when a developer chooses to hide some complex Hypertext Transfer Protocol(HTTP) or a case of adding essential functions. So now comes the question what Laravel web development is, it is a PHP framework that has been built with the focus to write computer code which is simple and expensive as well. It’s the highly used and again the modern web application framework that is freely available. Laravel web development is well known to have been used in creating personalized web software in a quick and efficient way.</span></font><br>', '<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; display: inline !important;\">FrontEnd Engineer Course :&nbsp;</span>', '1970-01-01', '1970-01-01', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(31, 20, 'FULL STACK IN ASP.NET', 'الدورة الشاملة في ال ASP.NET', '<span style=\"color: rgb(45, 52, 56); font-family: Bahij-TheSansArabic-SemiLight; letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243); display: inline !important;\">ASP “Active Server Pages” is the most secure robust server side technology to build enterprise-class web applications with a minimum number of coding. ASP.NET is part of the .NET Framework and by using it; you can code your applications in any language compatible with the common language runtime (CLR), including Microsoft Visual Basic and C#.&nbsp;</span><br style=\"color: rgb(45, 52, 56); font-family: Bahij-TheSansArabic-SemiLight; letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 52, 56); font-family: Bahij-TheSansArabic-SemiLight; letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243); display: inline !important;\">ASP.NET MVC - Level 1 course includes step by step instructions, classroom exercises and discussions to have a basic level of knowledge in using the following techniques: (T-SQL, C# ,OOP, Control Structure , ADO.NET, HTML , JS, ASP.NET C# , ADO.NET, HTML 5, CSS2, CSS3, Repeater , Stored Procedure , Multiview, Web user Control ,IIS, JQUERY ).</span>', '<span style=\"color: rgb(45, 52, 56); font-family: Bahij-TheSansArabic-SemiLight; font-size: 15px; text-align: right; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243); display: inline !important;\">تعد صفحات الخادم النشط - ASP.net أكثر التقنيات أمانًا للعمل على محركات الخوادم لصفحات الويب الديناميكية وإنشاء تطبيقات الويب المختلفة بأقل عدد ممكن من الكودات المكتوبة, وتعد أيضاً جزءًا من فئة .net ومن خلال استخدامه؛ يتمكن المستخدمون من برمجة التطبيقات بأي لغة متوافقة مع وقت تشغيل اللغة الشائعة CLR، بما في ذلك مايكروسوفت فيجيوال بيسيك Microsoft Visual Basic والسي شارب #C.&nbsp;</span><br style=\"color: rgb(45, 52, 56); font-family: Bahij-TheSansArabic-SemiLight; font-size: 15px; text-align: right; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 52, 56); font-family: Bahij-TheSansArabic-SemiLight; font-size: 15px; text-align: right; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243); display: inline !important;\">يتضمن المستوى الأول من الدورة تعليمات خطوة بخطوة وتمارين عملية ومناقشات لتمكين المتدربين من الحصول على المستوى الأساسي من المعرفة في استخدام التقنيات التالية: T-SQL، سي شارب C#, لغة البرمجة الكائنية OOP، هيكل التحكم ، ADO.NET ، HTML ،JS ،ASP.net C # ، ADO.net،HTML 5 ،CSS2 ،CSS3 ، IIS ، JQUERY ، ...وغيرها. ومن أجل ضمان تحقيق هذه المتدربين لأهداف الدورة، يتعين عليهم إعداد مشروع نهائي.</span>', '<ul><li><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 52, 56); font-family: Bahij-TheSansArabic-Plain; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243); letter-spacing: 0.5px; display: inline !important;\">Developing Microsoft ASP.Net.</span></li><li><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 52, 56); font-family: Bahij-TheSansArabic-Plain; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243); letter-spacing: 0.5px; display: inline !important;\">Getting the basic Techniques, skills and abilities in Microsoft and other third party tools to create dynamic website from scratch with the best performance and the best look and feel.</span></li><li><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 52, 56); font-family: Bahij-TheSansArabic-Plain; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243); letter-spacing: 0.5px; display: inline !important;\">To be familiar with the Web development process in general.</span></li><li><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 52, 56); font-family: Bahij-TheSansArabic-Plain; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243); letter-spacing: 0.5px; display: inline !important;\">Developing ASP.NET MVC 5 Web Applications.</span></li><li><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 52, 56); font-family: Bahij-TheSansArabic-Plain; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243); letter-spacing: 0.5px; display: inline !important;\">Learning advanced techniques, skills and abilities from Microsoft and other third party tools to create your professional and responsive website from scratch with the best performance and the good look and feel.</span></li></ul>', '<pre class=\"tw-data-text tw-ta tw-text-small\" data-placeholder=\"Translation\" id=\"tw-target-text\" data-fulltext=\"\" dir=\"rtl\" style=\"unicode-bidi: isolate; border: none; padding: 0px 0.14em 0px 0px; position: relative; margin-bottom: 0px; resize: none; font-family: inherit; overflow: hidden; text-align: right; width: 275px; white-space: pre-wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(33, 33, 33); height: 264px; font-size: 16px !important; line-height: 24px !important;\">تطوير مايكروسوفت ASP.Net.\r\nالحصول على التقنيات والمهارات والقدرات الأساسية في Microsoft وغيرها من أدوات الطرف الثالث لإنشاء موقع ديناميكي من البداية مع أفضل أداء وأفضل مظهر ومظهر.\r\nأن تكون على دراية بعملية تطوير الويب بشكل عام.\r\nتطوير ASP.NET MVC 5 تطبيقات الويب.\r\nتعلم التقنيات المتقدمة والمهارات والقدرات من Microsoft وغيرها من أدوات الطرف الثالث لإنشاء موقع ويب احترافي وسريع الاستجابة من البداية مع أفضل أداء وشكل ومظهر جيد.<br><br><br><ul><li><br></li><li><br></li></ul><br><span tabindex=\"0\" lang=\"ar\"></span></pre>', '1', 30, '1552911012-Untitled-18906.jpg', '200', '50', '<span class=\"text_exposed_show\" style=\"display: inline; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: black; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">FrontEnd Engineer\r\nCourse :&nbsp;</span><br>\r\n<span class=\"6qdm\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \" segoe=\"\" ui=\"\" symbol\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" black;=\"\" background-image:=\"\" initial;=\"\" background-position:=\"\" background-siz